The paper discusses multiple human tracking using RGB-D data, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of depth cues also involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses benchmark datasets and comparative evaluations, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
